[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":319},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fhexo\u002F20200916\u002F4257870076\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fhexo\u002F20200916\u002F4257870076\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fhexo\u002F20200916\u002F4257870076\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fhexo\u002F20200916\u002F4257870076\u002F":296,"related:\u002Fhexo\u002F20200916\u002F4257870076\u002F":305},"\u002Fen\u002Fhexo\u002F2020\u002F09\u002F16\u002Flearn-hexo-03-install-hexo\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":279,"date":280,"description":18,"extension":281,"lang":282,"meta":283,"navigation":284,"path":285,"readingMinutes":286,"seo":287,"standalone":288,"stem":289,"tags":290,"tldr":293,"updated":293,"url":294,"__hash__":295},"content\u002F試著學 Hexo\u002F3-試著學-Hexo-如何安裝-Hexo.md","(3) 試著學 Hexo - 如何安裝 Hexo","4257870076",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":273},"minimark",[11,15,19,22,25,28,35,41,44,64,67,70,76,79,82,97,101,104,107,131,134,140,143,152,155,166,169,175,178,187,193,196,200,208,211,223,228,231,239,244,247,255,260,263,269],[12,13,14],"h2",{"id":14},"前言",[16,17,18],"p",{},"接下來這一篇將會介紹兩種作業系統(Window、Mac)的安裝模式，但是後面的文章介紹與操作就會主要以 Mac 為主，基本上只有安裝的時候會稍微有一點不一樣而已，其餘後面的文章就沒有什麼太大差異。",[12,20,21],{"id":21},"起手式",[16,23,24],{},"首先在安裝 Hexo 之前我們必須先準備所謂的開發環境，前一篇文章中有介紹到 Hexo 是基於 Node.js 製作，因此 Node.js 就必須要安裝，此外這邊也會建議要安裝 Git，因為 Git 的安裝與否將會影響到後面的操作。",[16,26,27],{},"基本上你進入到 Node.js 與 Git 官方網站時，就會自己顯示相關作業系統的安裝，在這邊 Git 安裝方式就不額外介紹你可以稍微將 「Git 安裝」這個關鍵字拿去餵狗(Google)，因此這邊就只會介紹 Node.js 安裝",[16,29,30],{},[31,32],"img",{"alt":33,"src":34},"Mac OS","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FHexo\u002F%E8%A9%A6%E8%91%97%E5%AD%B8%20Hexo%20%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202020-07-11%2016.15.43.png",[16,36,37],{},[31,38],{"alt":39,"src":40},"Windows","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FHexo\u002F%E8%A9%A6%E8%91%97%E5%AD%B8%20Hexo%20%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97\u002F2020-07-11_16-19-07.png",[16,42,43],{},"而這邊說明一下 「LTS」與 「Current」 的意思",[45,46,47,56],"ul",{},[48,49,50,51],"li",{},"LTS\n",[45,52,53],{},[48,54,55],{},"中文是長期支援版 (Long-term support)，簡單來講就是當前且較穩定的版本。",[48,57,58,59],{},"Current\n",[45,60,61],{},[48,62,63],{},"中文是當前版，簡單來講就是目前最新的版本。",[16,65,66],{},"通常來講我們在實際開發專案是會建議使用 LTS 版本即可，除非你有什麼特別想嘗試的新功能才會去安裝 Current。",[16,68,69],{},"那我們該選擇哪一個 Node.js 版本呢？通常來講是選擇 LTS，如果真的不清楚的話，本篇我們將會使用 Hexo 4，那在前一篇文章有提到官方所提供的 Hexo 4 在各 Node.js 版本的表現速度",[16,71,72],{},[31,73],{"alt":74,"src":75},"Node.js 版本","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FHexo\u002F%E8%A9%A6%E8%91%97%E5%AD%B8%20Hexo%20%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202020-07-11%2016.28.38.png",[16,77,78],{},"因此剛好現在 LTS 是 12 所以就可以直接挑選 LTS 安裝即可。",[16,80,81],{},"假使你電腦中有相當多 Node.js 版本可能會切換來切換去，那麼就會建議你可以參考以下文章的解決方式，我本身也是使用 nvm 來切換版本，所以也推薦給你",[45,83,84,91],{},[48,85,86],{},[87,88,90],"a",{"href":89},"\u002Fnodejs\u002F20200124\u002F3404456418\u002F","Mac OS X 安裝 nvm",[48,92,93],{},[87,94,96],{"href":95},"\u002Fnodejs\u002F20200107\u002F3738078915\u002F","Windows 10 安裝並使用 nvm 切換 NodeJS 版本",[12,98,100],{"id":99},"mac-安裝-hexo","Mac 安裝 Hexo",[16,102,103],{},"接下來讓我們打開終端機，你可以搜尋 「Terminal.app」 或是「終端機」也可以，因為我本身是使用 iTerm，所以就直接用該終端機來展示(只是介面比較漂亮而已)。",[16,105,106],{},"準備開始安裝 Hexo 之前會建議你先執行以下指令，確定 Node.js 版本以及 npm 是否已經正確安裝(npm 會隨著 Node.js 安裝時一起安裝)",[108,109,114],"pre",{"className":110,"code":111,"language":112,"meta":113,"style":113},"language-cmd shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","node -v\nnpm -v\n","cmd","",[115,116,117,125],"code",{"__ignoreMap":113},[118,119,122],"span",{"class":120,"line":121},"line",1,[118,123,124],{},"node -v\n",[118,126,128],{"class":120,"line":127},2,[118,129,130],{},"npm -v\n",[16,132,133],{},"如果都有跳出版本號，那麼就是成功安裝，舉例來講，我們目前應該顯示的 Node.js 版本應該要是 LTS 版本的 12，那麼 Node.js 理應出現的版本會是 v12.18.2(npm 版本影響不大，只是要確保有安裝 npm，否則會無法安裝套件)。",[16,135,136],{},[31,137],{"alt":138,"src":139},"Node 版本","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FHexo\u002F%E8%A9%A6%E8%91%97%E5%AD%B8%20Hexo%20%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202020-07-11%2016.39.49.png",[16,141,142],{},"接下來讓我們在終端機輸入以下指令開始安裝 Hexo",[108,144,146],{"className":110,"code":145,"language":112,"meta":113,"style":113},"npm install -g hexo-cli\n",[115,147,148],{"__ignoreMap":113},[118,149,150],{"class":120,"line":121},[118,151,145],{},[16,153,154],{},"基本上 Mac 在安裝時有可能會遇到一些問題，這一段問題在官方有說明，因此我這邊直接貼上官方說明",[156,157,158],"blockquote",{},[16,159,160,161,165],{},"您在編譯時可能會碰到問題，請先至 App Store 安裝 Xcode，一旦 Xcode 安裝完成後，開啟它並前往 ",[162,163,164],"strong",{},"Preferences -> Download -> Command Line Tools -> Install"," 安裝命令列工具。",[16,167,168],{},"通常如果你有安裝 Git 應該是不太會出現該錯誤訊息。",[16,170,171],{},[31,172],{"alt":173,"src":174},"安裝 Hexo","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FHexo\u002F%E8%A9%A6%E8%91%97%E5%AD%B8%20Hexo%20%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202020-07-11%2016.45.24.png",[16,176,177],{},"接下來讓我們在終端機上輸入以下指令",[108,179,181],{"className":110,"code":180,"language":112,"meta":113,"style":113},"hexo -v\n",[115,182,183],{"__ignoreMap":113},[118,184,185],{"class":120,"line":121},[118,186,180],{},[16,188,189],{},[31,190],{"alt":191,"src":192},"Hexo 版本","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FHexo\u002F%E8%A9%A6%E8%91%97%E5%AD%B8%20Hexo%20%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202020-07-11%2020.45.28.png",[16,194,195],{},"恭喜你，當你出現上面的圖片的資訊，就代表你已經成功安裝 Hexo。",[12,197,199],{"id":198},"windows-安裝-hexo","Windows 安裝 Hexo",[16,201,202,203,207],{},"而在 Windows 的安裝上其實並沒有太大的差異，在這邊終端機我會使用「PowerShell」作為示範，當然你可能會問我為什麼我的 PowerShell 比較漂亮，那是因為我使用的是「Windows Terminal」，你可以透過 Microsoft Store 安裝，若你對於美化有興趣的話，你也可以參考我這一篇文章「",[87,204,206],{"href":205},"\u002Fother\u002F20190924\u002F3446878284\u002F","Window PowerShell美化(Windows Terminal)","」",[16,209,210],{},"回歸正題，當你開啟 Windows Terminal 之後，會建議你一樣先養成習慣確認一下自己目前電腦的 Node 版本以及是否安裝 npm",[108,212,213],{"className":110,"code":111,"language":112,"meta":113,"style":113},[115,214,215,219],{"__ignoreMap":113},[118,216,217],{"class":120,"line":121},[118,218,124],{},[118,220,221],{"class":120,"line":127},[118,222,130],{},[16,224,225],{},[31,226],{"alt":138,"src":227},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FHexo\u002F%E8%A9%A6%E8%91%97%E5%AD%B8%20Hexo%20%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97\u002F2020-07-12_21-37-07.png",[16,229,230],{},"接下來與前面 Mac 相同輸入以下指令安裝 Hexo",[108,232,233],{"className":110,"code":145,"language":112,"meta":113,"style":113},[115,234,235],{"__ignoreMap":113},[118,236,237],{"class":120,"line":121},[118,238,145],{},[16,240,241],{},[31,242],{"alt":173,"src":243},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FHexo\u002F%E8%A9%A6%E8%91%97%E5%AD%B8%20Hexo%20%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97\u002F2020-07-12_21-40-28.png",[16,245,246],{},"安裝完畢之後一樣可以透過以下指令確認是否已經安裝成功",[108,248,249],{"className":110,"code":180,"language":112,"meta":113,"style":113},[115,250,251],{"__ignoreMap":113},[118,252,253],{"class":120,"line":121},[118,254,180],{},[16,256,257],{},[31,258],{"alt":191,"src":259},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FHexo\u002F%E8%A9%A6%E8%91%97%E5%AD%B8%20Hexo%20%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97\u002F2020-07-12_21-39-59.png",[16,261,262],{},"當你看到上圖相關資訊之後，就代表你成功安裝囉。",[16,264,265,266],{},"那麼今天鐵人賽就先到這邊結束，也恭喜你完成 Hexo 安裝，我們下一篇見囉 ",[267,268],"d",{},[270,271,272],"style",{},"html .default .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}",{"title":113,"searchDepth":127,"depth":127,"links":274},[275,276,277,278],{"id":14,"depth":127,"text":14},{"id":21,"depth":127,"text":21},{"id":99,"depth":127,"text":100},{"id":198,"depth":127,"text":199},"Hexo","2020-09-16 10:47:28","md","zh-Hant",{},true,"\u002Fhexo\u002F3-hexo-hexo","3",{"title":6,"description":18},false,"試著學 Hexo\u002F3-試著學-Hexo-如何安裝-Hexo",[279,291,292],"試著學 Hexo","第 12 屆 iT邦幫忙鐵人賽",null,"\u002Fhexo\u002F20200916\u002F4257870076\u002F","vdVReKf6yxqqFlColbvvBMAS0KIV8NSKkcy1Ka_GSFw",{"newer":297,"older":301},{"url":298,"title":299,"date":300},"\u002Fhexo\u002F20200917\u002F636983586\u002F","(4) 試著學 Hexo - 認識 Hexo 目錄結構","2020-09-17 08:24:47",{"url":302,"title":303,"date":304},"\u002Fhexo\u002F20200915\u002F1337908132\u002F","(2) 試著學 Hexo - 什麼是 Hexo","2020-09-15 00:00:10",[306,311,315],{"url":307,"title":308,"date":309,"readingMinutes":310},"\u002Fhexo\u002F20221030\u002F561405053\u002F","解決 Hexo 更新系統或使用 CI 部署後文章出現更新日期的問題","2022-10-30 11:52:35","2",{"url":312,"title":313,"date":314,"readingMinutes":286},"\u002Fhexo\u002F20201101\u002F60919\u002F","(33)試著學 Hexo-番外篇之更新 NexT 主題","2020-11-01 13:21:00",{"url":316,"title":317,"date":318,"readingMinutes":310},"\u002Fhexo\u002F20201031\u002F2194088152\u002F","(32)試著學 Hexo-番外篇之更新 Hexo","2020-10-31 14:01:51",1784020385725]